These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, sprite, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, rugby, badminton
1. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
2. the person drinking cola is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person drinking sprite##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola   | almond-milk    | tea    | sprite |
| Sport      | badminton | cricket | rugby | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, cola, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, kiwi, corn, nectarine
1. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
3. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
4. the person drinking fanta is not the person eating kiwi##6
5. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating corn##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | fanta  | cola    | 7up | soy-milk    |
| Food       | nectarine | kiwi | corn  | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, coffee, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, firefighter, security-guard, librarian
1. the person drinking almond-milk is not the fisherman##6
2. the firefighter is not the person drinking coffee##6
3. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
4. the firefighter is the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the firefighter##1
6. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
7. the fisherman is on the far left or far right##3
8. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk       | juice  | 7up  | coffee |
| Job        | security-guard | librarian | firefighter | fisherman  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, rabbit, bird, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, tram, helicopter, taxi
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
3. the person driving the taxi is not the owner of the rabbit##6
4. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | rabbit | bird | frog     | rat |
| Transport   | tram     | helicopter    | motorbike | taxi    |

