.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, sprite, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, train, taxi, airplane
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
3. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
4. the person drinking cola is not the person driving the airplane##6
5. the person driving the tram is not the person drinking juice##6
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | juice        | water | sprite | cola |
| Transport   | airplane | tram | train     | taxi   |

