.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, comedy, drama, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, egyptian, turkish, french
1. the pakistani is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is not the egyptian##6
3. the pakistani is on the far right##1
4. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the french##5
5. the person watching drama movies is the person watching drama movies##1
6. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
7. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
8. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the french##5
9. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the french##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | drama    | horror  | epic   |
| Nationality   | turkish  | french | egyptian | pakistani |

