.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, comedy, western, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, folk, hip-hop, r&b
1. the fan hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan disco##3
2. the fan hip-hop is not the person watching comedy movies##6
3. the person watching epic movies is the fan folk##1
4. the fan disco is on the left or right of the fan r&b##3
5. the fan hip-hop is on the far left##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is the fan disco##1
7. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the fan disco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy     | western | epic |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | disco | r&b      | folk         |

