.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, hot-chocolate, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, scientist, fisherman, architect
1. the videographer is on the left of the scientist##1
2. the architect is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
3. the architect is on the right of the scientist##1
4. the scientist is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the scientist##3
6. the videographer is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
7. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
8. the person drinking fanta is not the architect##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | fanta  | mirinda        | hot-chocolate      | juice          |
| Job        | videographer | scientist | architect | fisherman |

