.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, doctor, accountant, freelancer
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, trike, ship, tram
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the trike is not the freelancer##6
3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5
4. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the tram is the accountant##1
7. the police-officer is not the person driving the tram##6
8. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the freelancer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | police-officer  | accountant | freelancer    | doctor |
| Transport   | trike | tram | ship | train  |

