.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, hamster, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, sailing, basketball, handball
1. the person who's sport is skiing is not the owner of the goat##6
2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the owner of the hamster is not the person who's sport is handball##6
6. the person who's sport is sailing is not the owner of the goldfish##6
7. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hamster | goat        | snake  | goldfish     |
| Sport   | skiing     | handball | sailing | basketball |

