.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, photography, skydiving, hiking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, funk, jazz, punk
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
2. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
3. the fan jazz is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6
4. the person who's hobby is photography is between the fan punk and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the fan funk is between the fan house and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | photography    | drawing | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | house         | funk | punk   | jazz     |

