.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, plum, papaya, radish
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, subway, motorbike
1. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
2. the person eating radish is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
3. the person driving the taxi is the person eating radish##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the person driving the subway is not the person eating radish##6
6. the person eating plum is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
7. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
8. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | apricot  | papaya | plum | radish |
| Transport   | subway | quad-bike     | motorbike     | taxi    |

