.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, corn, papaya, orange
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, fantasy, family, scientific
1. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5
2. the person eating corn is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
3. the person eating lime is the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
5. the person eating lime is between the person eating corn and the person watching superhero movies##2
6. the person eating corn is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | orange | corn      | lime | papaya   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | family | scientific   | superhero |

