The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, thriller, action, time-travel
1. the person watching action movies is not the person drinking 7up##6
2. the person watching action movies is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | 7up       | juice | almond-milk     | sprite     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | action       | time-travel | thriller |

