4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the designer and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the designer is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
7. the chef is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | lawyer  | police-officer | chef | designer |
| Sport   | swimming | ice-hockey | parkour   | weightlifting |

