.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, writing, dancing, rock-climbing
4 different pets are kept: dog, snake, ferret, rabbit
1. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
2. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is writing##2
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | writing | dancing | reading | rock-climbing |
| Pet     | ferret  | snake      | dog  | rabbit       |

