2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
3. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the car is not the person drinking juice##6
5. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
6. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice | fanta | sprite      | cola   |
| Transport   | helicopter  | ship   | van | car |

 